name: Agent
line: Rick, we're taking fire from an automated turret. Can you bring it offline?

name: Rick
line: You're a good boy, Morty. You've done a good thing tonight.

name: Agent
line: Oh, for crying out—he cried because he didn't give me enough milk.

name: Rick
line: It's okay, Morty, it's okay to be angry. Just don't move, don't speak, don’t think, donut.

name: Rick
line: Don't worry about Jerry. He'll be fine. Just stay out of this. You know, he knows Jerry is a terrorist. He wants us to be okay.

name: Agent
line: Jerry, we just got him back.
